<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
      <h1 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello <%= @user.email.split('@').first.capitalize %>,</h1>
      
      <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Here are your journaling questions for today:</p>
      
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #495057; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Question 1</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><%= @prompt.question_1 %></p>
        
        <h2 style="color: #495057; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Question 2</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;"><%= @prompt.question_2 %></p>
      </div>
      
      <div style="background-color: #e7f3ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>How to reply:</strong> Simply reply to this email with your thoughts. Write freely—there's no strict format required. Your response will be saved as a journal entry.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
        Happy journaling!<br>
        — Inbox Journal
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
